reviewText:
I usually don't write reviews, but i must for this special collection set, it deserves my time.
The quality of this 12 Volume Rascals Collection is the best uncut version i ever seen.
The container Box is carefully designed with an Elegant touch, not a Plastic cheap Box, i strongly suggest to anyone looking for best quality at reasonable price!!!
He loves the video he watches them every nite.
I remember watching all of them in the early 60s

I literally cried when I found this! My brother & I use to watch them (on vhs) when we were kids. It brought back great memories. My husband had never watched them so we sit & watch them now. And when our little one is old enough, we'll sit & watch as a family!
Good quality shows at a good price. Very pleased.
Absolute classic and a must have for us who grew up watching Our Gang on TV.
These titles are not public domain.  They are under copyright, and this set is unlicensed and illegally produced.  There is a legitimate release of these that we should support.
excellent. but did not like the cover. should have been a box set.
Great DVD 's  wishing there were more episodes.  Very fast delivery  five star for me
